Results for ZeroSpeech2017 Track 2
==================================

In the `segmentation/` directory of
<https://github.com/kamperh/recipe_zs2017_track2>, the following was executed
for the different languages:

    # Mandarin
    ./ksegment.py \
        --K_max 0.1landmarks \
        --min_duration 5 \
        --init_am_n_iter 0 \
        --segment_n_iter 5 \
        --n_slices_max 4 \
        --p_boundary_init 0.5 \
        --n_cpus 15 \
        --n_batches 5 \
        data/mandarin/mfcc.n_10.n_max_4.unsup_syl

